{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782166037830,"sessionID":"ses_10ea0a9e0ffeWcdjIUpwYHN6pT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"676087857","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-22T19-55-04-956Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-1/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates and returns a cache object with storage methods.\n\n```javascript\nimport { createCache } from './cache.mjs'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves and returns the cached value for a given key. Returns `undefined` if the key does not exist.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The cache key to retrieve\n\n**Returns:** The cached value or `undefined`\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache under the given key. Returns the stored value.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The cache key to store the value under\n- `value` - The value to cache\n\n**Returns:** The stored value\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves a cached value for the given key.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The cache key to delete\n\n**Returns:** `true` if the key was deleted, `false` otherwise\n\n### clear()\n\nClears all entries from the cache.\n\n**Returns:** `undefined`\n\n## Implementation\n\nThe cache uses a `Map` internally for O(1) storage and retrieval operations.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-22T19-55-04-956Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-1/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","exists":false,"truncated":false,"tokenwarden":{"wouldHaveUsedTokens":6,"usedTokens":6,"savedTokens":0,"percentSaved":0,"rawPath":"/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-22T19-55-04-956Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-1/tokenwarden/encrypted/raw-tool-output/ses_10ea0a9e0ffeWcdjIUpwYHN6pT/676087857.txt.enc","event":{"timestamp":"2026-06-22T22:07:17.808Z","sessionID":"ses_10ea0a9e0ffeWcdjIUpwYHN6pT","source":"tool-output","label":"write","wouldHaveUse